OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779711070
OL,3,CTearful Mo Salah says goodbye to
OL,4,CLiverpool after nine years
OL,6,FIt ended with tears and a final kiss
OL,7,Fof the Anfield turf - as Mohamed Salah
OL,8,Fsaid goodbye to Liverpool's fans after
OL,9,Fnine years full of goals and glory.
OL,11,FThe Egyptian King admitted he had
OL,12,F"cried more than in my entire life"
OL,13,Fafter playing his last match for the
OL,14,FReds on a sun-drenched Sunday against
OL,15,FBrentford.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
