FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779711070
OL,3,CTearful Mo Salah says goodbye to
OL,4,CLiverpool after nine years
OL,6,FAnd of course, Salah being Salah, he
OL,7,Falso played a major part in the final
OL,8,Fmatch of the 2025-26 Premier League
OL,9,Fseason, providing the assist for
OL,10,FCurtis Jones' opener and missing by
OL,11,Finches as he sought to add to his 193
OL,12,FPremier League goals when his free-
OL,13,Fkick hit a post in the first half.
OL,15,FManager Arne Slot, whose relationship
OL,16,Fwith Salah has clearly become strained
OL,17,Fthis season, awarded him the adulation
OL,18,Fhe clearly deserved by substituting
OL,19,Fhim in the 74th minute, a signal for
OL,20,Fthe whole crowd to rise to its feet.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779711070
OL,3,CTearful Mo Salah says goodbye to
OL,4,CLiverpool after nine years
OL,6,FSalah's team-mates gave him an
OL,7,Fimpromptu guard of honour and he knelt
OL,8,Fto kiss the turf one final time before
OL,9,Ftaking his seat on the bench.
OL,11,FAfter the final whistle blew on the 1-
OL,12,F1 draw which secured Champions League
OL,13,Ffootball next season, Salah told Sky
OL,14,FSports: "I think I've cried more than
OL,15,Fin my whole life. I'm not really an
OL,16,Femotional guy."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779711070
OL,3,CTearful Mo Salah says goodbye to
OL,4,CLiverpool after nine years
OL,6,FStanding next to left-back Andy
OL,7,FRobertson, who was also saying goodbye
OL,8,Fafter a nine-year stay at Anfield,
OL,9,FSalah added: "We lived our youth here,
OL,10,Fsharing everything from the beginning
OL,11,Fto the end. We put this club back
OL,12,Fwhere it belongs.
OL,14,F"It's tricky to leave Liverpool. It's
OL,15,Flife. I look back and wonder if I
OL,16,Fwould have wanted more than I
OL,17,Fachieved. Not really. We won it all.
OL,19,F"We see the love from the fans and
OL,20,Fthis is the most important thing for
OL,21,Fme.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779711070
OL,3,CTearful Mo Salah says goodbye to
OL,4,CLiverpool after nine years
OL,6,F"I will be far away from here. I will
OL,7,Fbe emotional every time. I hope the
OL,8,Fteam stays in the position, fighting
OL,9,Ffor everything."
OL,11,FThe narrative of Salah becoming the
OL,12,Fclub's leading Premier League assist
OL,13,Frecord holder with his 93rd was
OL,14,Fspoiled somewhat by Kevin Schade's
OL,15,Fequaliser.
OL,17,F"Again we didn't get what we deserved
OL,18,Fand that is a common theme this
OL,19,Fseason, we deserved to win," said head
OL,20,Fcoach Arne Slot.
OL,26,@qD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779711070
OL,3,CTearful Mo Salah says goodbye to
OL,4,CLiverpool after nine years
OL,6,F"Although in the 100th minute we could
OL,7,Fhave lost it as they get a serious
OL,8,Fchance and it didn't go in.
OL,10,F"We came here today to do the minimum
OL,11,Frequired and when you look at the
OL,12,Fleague table, big clubs are not able
OL,13,Fto qualify for the Champions League or
OL,14,FEurope so we can not take it for
OL,15,Fgranted ` but it is clear and obvious
OL,16,Fwe wanted more.
OL,18,F"But I am proud of the players because
OL,19,Fit has been a very difficult season."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
